### Search Service API Tests

### 1. Basic Search by Keyword
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "swift",
  "page": 0,
  "size": 10
}

### 2. Search by Brand and City
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### 3. Search with Price Range
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minPrice": 300000,
  "maxPrice": 700000,
  "fuelType": "PETROL",
  "page": 0,
  "size": 20
}

### 4. Search by Year Range
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minYear": 2018,
  "maxYear": 2023,
  "transmission": "AUTOMATIC"
}

### 5. Location-based Search (Geo-spatial)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 19.0760,
  "longitude": 72.8777,
  "radiusKm": 50,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### 6. Advanced Search with Multiple Filters
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "fuelType": "PETROL",
  "transmission": "MANUAL",
  "minPrice": 400000,
  "maxPrice": 600000,
  "maxOdometer": 50000,
  "minYear": 2019,
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "status": "AVAILABLE",
  "sortBy": "basePrice",
  "sortDirection": "ASC"
}

### 7. Simple GET Search
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles?keyword=swift&brand=Maruti%20Suzuki&page=0&size=10

### 8. Search by City (GET)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/search/vehicles?city=Mumbai&page=0&size=20
